data.enText: to appear again after not being heard of or seen for a period of time

data.chText: 她上了楼，直到第二天早晨才再次露面。
data.enText: She went upstairs and did not reappear until morning.

simple_means.memory_skill: re 一再，重新 + appear 出现 → 再出现

example: The sores reappeared on her body
Her husband reappeared after having left her years ago

value.def: When people or things reappear, they return again after they have been away or out of sight for some time.

example.ex: Thirty seconds later she reappeared and beckoned them forward.
example.tran: 30秒后她又出现了，示意他们往前来。
